commit.message: made it so that no-text will articulate properly for word divisions on notes
updated README with command-line flags for running program
added the ability to sing songs on a single vowel (ah), and also added deck the halls to the list of sheet music
fixed bug where tempo only the first tempo would be used in a song
added the ability to change tempos. Also adjusted TTS prosidy to make recordings sound better, and created new demos for all of the examples
added sing we and chant it by thomas morley as an example
cleaned up sheet music folder, and added two more example performances
removed old items from todo list
added gitkeep files to folders that need to not be deleted
removed old folder from project structure
fixed several issued including silence that was added before and after notes. Also cleaned up directory structure a bit
added ability to merge tied notes into a single note event
updated saving to not overwrite older files
cleaned up project repo, and made some modifications to settings
initial commit of project to git
